    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your <strong>potato[es] </strong>(skins on) into fries</p><p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p><p>Put a separate large baking tray in the oven with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>to heat up</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hoisin-king-oyster-mushroom-bao-with-sesame-sweet-potato-fries/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Pull your <strong>king oyster mushrooms </strong>lengthways into long thick strands</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hoisin-king-oyster-mushroom-bao-with-sesame-sweet-potato-fries/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>five-spice mix </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> in a large bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>pulled king oyster mushroom </strong>to the bowl and give everything a good mix up until fully coated</p><p>Once coated, add your <strong>cornflour </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and give it all stir until covered in the flour</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hoisin-king-oyster-mushroom-bao-with-sesame-sweet-potato-fries/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Remove the preheated baking tray from the oven, add your <strong>floured mushroom</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-17 min or until golden and crispy</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hoisin-king-oyster-mushroom-bao-with-sesame-sweet-potato-fries/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>cucumber </strong>finely</p><p>Add the<strong> sliced cucumber</strong> to a small bowl with your<strong> rice vinegar </strong>and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up and set aside to pickle - this is your <strong>pickled cucumber</strong></p><p>Trim and chop your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> in half, then cut lengthways into thin strips</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hoisin-king-oyster-mushroom-bao-with-sesame-sweet-potato-fries/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and <strong>gluten free soy sauce </strong>in a small bowl with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong></p><p>Once your mushroom is crispy and cooked, stir through <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>hoisin sauce </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>hoisin king oyster mushroom</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hoisin-king-oyster-mushroom-bao-with-sesame-sweet-potato-fries/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Pierce your <strong>bao bun packet[s]</strong> with a few holes and <strong>microwave</strong> for 1-2 min</p><p>Once your chips are done, sprinkle <strong>most </strong>of your <strong>toasted sesame seeds </strong>over (save some for garnish!) \u2013 these are your <strong>sesame fries</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hoisin-king-oyster-mushroom-bao-with-sesame-sweet-potato-fries/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>To build, fill each <strong>warmed bao bun</strong> with some of the <strong>pickled cucumber</strong>, the <strong>hoisin king oyster mushroom</strong>, and the <strong>remaining hoisin sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped spring onion </strong>and the <strong>remaining toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>sesame fries </strong>and the <strong>remaining pickled cucumber </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
